title: CeeLo Greens The Good Life S01E01 I Love You Youre Hired WEB-DL
description:
TBS has ordered six episodes of the unscripted series, which will follow CeeLo as he tackles not only a packed schedule of producing, recording and performing, but also a creative partnership with his longtime best friends - Big Gipp, Khujoand T-Mo - as they prepare to bring their legendary hip-hop group Goodie Mob back to the world stage.


Episode 1 I Love You...You're Hired!
CeeLo and the Goodie Mob launch a luxury chauffeur service. CeeLo gets to throw out the opening pitch at a baseball game.
